{"tid":165571,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"到底白色個啲係咩嚟","createTime":"2017-03-21T12:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T13:08:27.000Z","uid":73612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41dc1f59df6088ba4b1a7a90817ab26b2c8be379","tid":165571,"uid":73612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T12:43:36.000Z","msg":"曾經係日本食過好似吉野家之類嘅連鎖牛肉飯店<br />\n咁唔識日文緊係睇圖叫<br />\n睇到有個牛肉飯上面有堆白色野<br />\n咁難得去到日本 <br />\n緊係食啲香港無嘅嘢<br />\n點知一試 原來凍嘅 而且仲好腥 <br />\n難食到即刻嘔出尼<br />\n到依家都好想知道係咩嚟<br />\n有無ching知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91752e798bb65fd96f0c6d0f6f420148796da5d0","tid":165571,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T12:44:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"401ec7c75540fd38c29e14512a825d816afc409c","tid":165571,"uid":73612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T12:47:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>精</blockquote><br />\n我都實估到有人會咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但真心問<br />\n想知咩嚟"},{"pid":"070842b56041967078bcfba434715ae5f5a1842c","tid":165571,"uid":47196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T12:47:29.000Z","msg":"以為白色珍珠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e1bf814ca793b00fda2cbce66d778ee598ab35","tid":165571,"uid":38602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T12:55:28.000Z","msg":"山藥"},{"pid":"860f5a20c0cdd54e876e1b5eb7099fb1fed5833c","tid":165571,"uid":73612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T12:59:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>山藥</blockquote><br />\n山藥？"},{"pid":"a45c9abb40ff7fc987eb93ad15d3edd9aa60e505","tid":165571,"uid":73612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:02:06.000Z","msg":"唔係一片片<br />\n一開頭以為忌廉𠴱類<br />\n同埋我記得佢有送芥末"},{"pid":"783dbdf02197da49bc27e68e3ec77bedcb7bc1e8","tid":165571,"uid":72796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:02:59.000Z","msg":"佢唔小心落左隻溫柔蛋，之後醒起你係買cheap啲個隻，然後用口吸返走，但吸唔乾淨，留低啲蛋白同口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca0a0d18f09e5d9238239c58aec2e82eebbebc4","tid":165571,"uid":40486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:03:12.000Z","msg":"淮山蓉 通便好啊"},{"pid":"4c04940c5305ad9c24829f990ddffa244c009e12","tid":165571,"uid":72796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:03:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢唔小心落左隻溫<span style=\"color: red;\">泉</span>蛋，之後醒起你係買cheap啲個隻，然後用口吸返走，但吸唔乾淨，留低啲蛋白同口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"20ae0bb4a7c6237799fada415ee699cf3c6d2c19","tid":165571,"uid":635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:03:52.000Z","msg":"這就是我們的白色珍珠"},{"pid":"23d1199af8f429fe144c6005b1c056bf3a0db7d7","tid":165571,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:04:11.000Z","msg":"とろろ"},{"pid":"c6692c147f78fd63209ca82a835bfa6b7937d9c4","tid":165571,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>山藥</blockquote><br />\n山藥？</blockquote><br />\n即係淮山磨蓉"},{"pid":"497733c4afe2ec5851bf2a4d1d1a340476e269d7","tid":165571,"uid":73612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:08:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>とろろ</blockquote><br />\n上網睇過圖<br />\n真係類似嘅野<br />\n如果我話佢又腥又難食<br />\n係咪好過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我成碗飯都食唔落"}]}